title: Episode 272: Nips and Knees (Feat. Kranium)
itunes:title: Episode 272: Nips and Knees (Feat. Kranium)
description:
Reggae and Dancehall singer, Kranium, joins the ladies of Lip Service this week to promote his latest singles including “Gal Policy” featuring Tiwa Savage, "Through the Window,” & “Everytime.” Kranium opens up about the different types of sexual pleasures he enjoys, why he likes toxic relationships, the craziest lie he’s ever said to go cheat, and much more. Enjoy!
